<c74object name="abc.hoa.binaural~" module="abclib">
  <digest>Abclib's High Order Ambisonics (HOA) Binaural Decoder based on the code of P.Lecomte</digest>
  <description><o>abc.hoa.binaural~</o> enable to decode from ambisonic spatial components using binaural decoder of P.Lecomte based on HRIR of the Neumann KU100 from 2D/3D ambisonics flux.
  <br /><br />
See Ambitools website : https://www.sekisushai.net/ambitools/<br />
And the paper : P. Lecomte, P.-A. Gauthier, C. Langrenne, A. Berry, et A. Garcia, « A Fifty-Node Lebedev Grid and Its Applications to Ambisonics », Journal of the Audio Engineering Society, vol. 64, nᵒ 11, p. 868‑881, 2016.
  </description>

  <!--INLETS-->
  <!-- <inletlist>
    <inlet id="0" type="INLET_TYPE">
